lead_paragraph: Having combined seamlessly for England, the players of Leicester City and Tottenham Hotspur will resume battle in the Premier League title race this weekend with the two main protagonists facing testing fixtures.

headline.print_headline: England Team Mates Set to Resume Title Rivalry
